rows.label: qev025902_MSG0001
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_JNK0010
rows.name: Verify

rows.label: qev025902_SEL0011
rows.name: Check Staccata for signs of life.

rows.label: qev025902_JNK0020
rows.name: Mourn

rows.label: qev025902_SEL0021
rows.name: Offer a prayer for the late doctor.

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0002
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0003
rows.name: I've been waiting for you, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0004
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0005
rows.name:
And just what are you praying to, hmm?
It better not be that damned Bringer of Miracles![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0006
rows.name: Phew...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0007
rows.name:
While I was playing dead, the actual bodies kept piling
up around me, you see? I'd about given up hope.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0008
rows.name:
Still, I think I knew you'd come, right? I'll have to thank
Jalimbo as well, once we get out of of of here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0009
rows.name:
Fraisie's further on inside, okay?
Please...stop her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0010
rows.name:
This no longer has anything to do with gods real or
imagined, does it? This is is is just slaughter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0011
rows.name:
Fraisie's been executing Ma-non as part of some...
ritual, hasn't she?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0012
rows.name:
But she's no zealot anymoreâ€”she's just a a a murderer.
You have to stop her, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0013
rows.name:
I don't know who that xenoform posing as a divine
avatar was, but you have to follow them and stop
them, don't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0014
rows.name:
If they go free, it will only mean more more more
Fraisies in the future, won't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0015
rows.name:
It's over, yes? The one responsible for luring in all those
Ma-non is gone? The one who tempted Fraisie into all
of this...madness?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0016
rows.name: I see... That's a relief, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0017
rows.name:
For all my skepticism, I never dreamed to suspect
that a shape-shifting xenoform was behind all this,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0018
rows.name:
You you you don't think there's a chance that any
other humans could be...you know? Impostors?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_JNK0030
rows.name: Assure

rows.label: qev025902_SEL0031
rows.name: Promise that you and your friends are real, at least.

rows.label: qev025902_JNK0040
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: qev025902_SEL0041
rows.name: Express concern about additional doppelgangers.

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0019
rows.name:
Oh no no no! It's abundantly clear that you're nothing
like their kind, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0020
rows.name:
Then I'll have to be more careful in the future, yes?
I won't allow any more Ma-non lives to be taken by
those scum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0021
rows.name:
Bringer of Miracles, grant me your guidance!
Purge these demons from your world![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0022
rows.name:
...It's over, Fraisie. There never was a Bringer of
Miracles, was there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0023
rows.name: LIES! I won't be tempted by your lies, demon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0024
rows.name:
I suppose that pitiful woman is a victim in this as well,
isn't she? But there's nothing I can do for her now, no?
I guess I'll leave the rest to you BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0025
rows.name: Let's go home, okay? Jalimbo will be worried.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0026
rows.name:
The Mediators took Fraisie into their custody, didn't
they? And she was still sure that her god would come
to rescue her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025902_MSG0027
rows.name:
For all her weakness and and and foolishness,
I can't help but pity her.[ST:wait ]
